{"tid":1479590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「我家哥哥出道幾千年」－人民日報叫人好似追星咁吹奏中國......","createTime":"2019-08-17T03:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T03:44:48.000Z","uid":286262,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9b751e454d38e6bb87302b6175869a87fc2cb55d","tid":1479590,"uid":286262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T03:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kqdjei8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkqdjei8.jpg&h=f9308cd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fm6Aw5P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFm6Aw5P.jpg&h=6cdd0fce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gS9yiLP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgS9yiLP.jpg&h=44738602&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6y7zNEa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6y7zNEa.jpg&h=4fc0c934&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dOKKpcr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdOKKpcr.jpg&h=9378d335&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人民日報叫緊D追星族用平時幫偶像打榜造勢、瘋狂留言呢類策略，翻牆吹奏國家同檢舉「港獨」FB page。「我家哥哥出道幾千年」呢D痴線野真係唔係正常人寫得出......<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但另一方面，亦有部份較理智既追星族開始發覺勢頭唔對。<br />\n<br />\n中共近年多番打壓D偶像團體，例如禁止D個樣太「娘」既男偶像上節目，又限制偶像選秀節目等等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/smLBfgn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsmLBfgn.png&h=6d25e0f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢排黨媒力推十四億護旗手、我支持香港警察呢類hashtag，一眾偶像團體例如TFBOYS、NINE PERCENT都要表態效忠，成班fans又要幫偶像護航。而家仲要擺明車馬要利用埋D fans。<br />\n<br />\n終於！有少女fans覺醒了！睇穿中共只係利用緊佢地同埋D明星，亦開始質疑呢類表態只係打飛機。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKFGYk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKFGYk.jpg&h=8fe23479&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wwTjc40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwwTjc40.jpg&h=5c5d059e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C3RQjK1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC3RQjK1.jpg&h=68c07be4&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nTeuAim.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnTeuAim.jpg&h=2e193834&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CFHWZK2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCFHWZK2.jpg&h=27fdfe76&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中共近來係咁搞呢D逼人表態既伎倆，只係反映出佢有幾咁不安。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Fascism is not the prohibition of saying things, it is the obligation to say them.&quot; - 哲學家Roland Barthes"},{"pid":"799a8a89607bdfddaa80fe11eea65dc7cfa63a88","tid":1479590,"uid":286262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T03:40:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6e949b54f41b207750351479342f2d4b7444de79","tid":1479590,"uid":157138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T03:44:48.000Z","msg":"作為一個官方媒體都咁撚智障，中國真係被一班低能仔管緊。 <br />\n<br />\nBtw，推番出面既818遊行post！"}]}